{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Journey to Incrementalia, become a necromancer willing to climb to unspeakable heights  of power to reach the treasures of Incrementalia, lost city of legend. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the accumulation of mana, the fuel of the gods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/extras/mana-600x260.gif?t=1731702023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cast diabolical spells and raise hellish minions to do your bidding (crush the walls).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/extras/clips-600x260.gif?t=1731702023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore skill synergies to unlock ridiculous builds. Experiment with freedom, skills can be reset at any time.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/extras/skills-600x260.gif?t=1731702023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And don't forget your old pal Bonesley, a very trustful and not-at-all treacherous skeleton servant! Here to help on your journey, as always...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Active Incremental gameplay: constantly grow to insane heights of power. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy all 99 walls with a nefarious array of invocations, encantations, skills and unique minions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play it your way: Active play is rewarded, or let it run idle to accumulate resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 70 skills, spells and abilities to uncover. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reset skills at any time to try out new builds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Summon thousands of minions and let them unleash hell.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go on whimsical side-quests and find legendary items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A not-so-serious story with an ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get to know Bonesley, your faithful skeleton minion that has no hidden agenda.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Synth dark fantasy soundtrack inspired by DOS classics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/extras/bottom-600x314.gif?t=1731702023\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Quartermaster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147430/89c4d20725b5e72307a05764defdd05e4e50a55d.jpg"},{"name":"Whoa-Ho! You're halfway the-ere!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147430/1c0537f33388bd03b29c99ff9fa6291885a2ca64.jpg"},{"name":"Purple Behelit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147430/32a5b27ad6c063f42a013578c11e2fea520fcd13.jpg"},{"name":"Journey's end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147430/b19801fdf020f0138f48a246e1f71c518efe2615.jpg"}],"total":4},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731702023","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/page.bg.jpg?t=1731702023","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/1c21909095ef639d9497477097ac901bdaa6bb54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731702023","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147430/1c21909095ef639d9497477097ac901bdaa6bb54/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731702023","categories":[{"description":"S